         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">14/11/88 ¶  ¶ Scleranthus ¶ , the small annual plant, dear Mr Tepper, I also have from a few other places for a long time. I intended to work on it carefully for the  ¶ Key ¶  but the work had to be e...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.11.14</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">14/11/88</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Privat</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>, die kleine einjährige Pflanze, lieber Herr Tepper, habe ich auch von einigen anderen Stellen seit längerer Zeit, wollte solche genau vornehmen für den "Key", aber die Arbeit musste beschleunigt werden, die Exhib. brach inzwischen darüber herein, u so liegen noch etwa 1 Dutz oder mehr Vict. Pfl., welche nicht aufgenommen werden konnten, obwohl <name key="Haloragis">Haloragis</name> u viel Anderes critisch fertig wurde.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe die Idee, dass es ein </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">eingeführtes</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name> sein mag, deren mehrere ich von Europe kenne. </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Halten</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Sie gefälligst die Pflanze einstweilen </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">zurück</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">. So wie die Ausstellung u der medicinische Congress vorüber sind, werde ich auch über diesen <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name> ins Klare kommen. Es würde nicht gut sein, diese Planze</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Pflanze.</p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> anderweitig zu vergeben, da ich etwa irrige (vielleicht bei der Mittenachts Lampe niedergeschriebene) Namen selbst in späterer Ruhe berichtigen kann.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Auch bitte ich etwaige Rückbleibsel von <name key="Pomatotheca">Pomatotheca</name> nicht abzugeben, da zwei Pflanzen untermischt zu sein scheinen in Ihren Exemplaren</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Freundschaftlich</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">14/11/88</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Private</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>
               </seg>, the small annual plant, dear Mr Tepper, I also have from a few other places for a long time. I intended to work on it carefully for the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Key</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B88.11.02.</p>
               </note> but the work had to be expedited, in the meantime the Exhibition<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Centennial International Exhibition, Melbourne, 1888-9.</p>
               </note> has overtaken it and so there are still another dozen or more Victorian plants that could not be included, although <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Haloragis">Haloragis</name>
               </seg> and many others were critically finished.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the idea that it may be an <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">introduced</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>
               </seg>, of which I know several from Europe. Kindly <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">retain</hi>
               </seg> the plants temporarily. As soon as the Exhibition and the medical congress<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Intercolonial Medical Congress, Melbourne, January 1889.</p>
               </note> are over, I'll also make up my mind about this <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>
               </seg>. It would not be good to assign this plant somewhere else since I can myself correct any wrong names (perhaps written down in the light of the midnight lamp) later at my leisure.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Also I ask not to give away eventual remainders of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Pomatotheca">Pomatotheca</name>
               </seg>, since two plants seem to be mixed in your specimens.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>See also M to O. Tepper, 17 November 1888.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Amicably</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Haloragis">Haloragis</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Pomatotheca">Pomatotheca</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
